<p class="indent">
  Equations <a href="#x1-5009r9">9</a> and <a href="#x1-5011r11">11</a> are compatible if
  
  <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML">
    <msub>
      <mrow>
        <mi>M</mi>
      </mrow>
      <mrow>
        <mn>1</mn>
