      </mrow>
      <mrow>
        <mn>1</mn>
      </mrow>
    </msub>
    <mi>ℚ</mi>
  </math>, leads to a symmetry change by generating a change of the algebraic nature of the transformation. We can distinguish three different situations:
</p>
<ol class="enumerate1">
  <li class="enumerate" id="x1-5013x1">
